name: CL Photography Logo
description:
Premade Fully Customizable Logo.

Pictured is the standard Logo. 
It has been created by me as a quick template for further design.
Once you purchase I will email you for all you options including changes in Name, Colour, size etc.
I am absolutely going to guarantee you are 100% happy before we finalize your design so I offer UNLIMITED changes on all my premade Designs with absolutely no extra charges.

If you have any questions you want answered before purchase please feel free to contact anytime.

Once final designs have been completed you will get your designs sent via USB In a range of formats including PS, AI, PNG, JPEG, PDF. Plus many more. If you need a certain format please let me know.

name: Formal/Wedding/Graduation Invitation
description:
These Invitations can be purchased as a Do It Yourself Printable only. 
You will get the file sent to your email. I will input all details including Guests, Location, RSVP etc.
Unlimited invitations.

All you have to do is print and deliver! Easy.

name: Formal Invitation
description:
Invitations can be purchased as a Do It Yourself Printable or as a fully finished Invitation Package.

A DIY printable I will send you the file for your invitation with you address, RSVP Details, Party date and time information and a saved file for each different child's name. You simply have to print them all out.

With the Finished Invitation Package ( up to 50 invitations, extra invitations will incur fees ) you will get fully finished Invitations details etc included. I will cut and adhere the invitations to 200gms Black card stock, Decorate the delivery envelopes with silver sealed stickers and address details. 
The pack will be posted to your work or home address. 
(Images provided of printed file and of finished package )
